Package: sdtmbuilder
Title: Metadata-Driven SDTM Domain Builder and Code Generator
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Chiara", "Cattani", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "chiara.cattani.it@gmail.com")
Description: Auto-generates SDTM domain programs (R scripts / Quarto documents)
    from structured metadata. Given SDTM target metadata (Study_Metadata.xlsx)
    and controlled terminology (Study_CT.xlsx), the package produces
    domain-building code for all SDTM domains with realistic derivations
    including merging multiple sources, controlled terminology assignment,
    ISO date/time handling, supplemental qualifier generation, and define.xml
    alignment. Source metadata is auto-inferred from raw data. Supports
    SDTM IG 3.4+ with sponsor-specific overrides via configuration.
